g.text: Noise at The Wayfinding Centre can vary depending on visitors and activities
Natural light is available throughout most of the centre, this can change with the weather
The colour of artificial lighting can be adjusted or turned off upon request
Street lights, traffic signals and heaters can also be turned off upon request
Sensory tools including ear defenders, fidgets, beanbags and blankets are available
Training Rooms can also be set up as a quiet space upon request
